This paper involves the application of an Artificial Immune System (AIS) to the task of film recommendation, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of Collaborative Filtering (CF) for recommendation, which is a common technique in Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with recommending films based on user preferences. The use of an AIS also involves self-organizing systems (cs.SI) and the optimization of the system (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.AI and cs.LG, followed by cs.IR, cs.SI, and cs.NE.
